      "ratingText": "Good",
      "reviewDate": "2023-12-14T02:09:00+07:00",
      "reviewTitle": "Good",
      "originalTitle": "",
      "originalComment": "Aku dapat kamar 01, ranjangnya bunyi2 ketika kita gerak, wlpun gerak sikit. Ternyata setelah aku cek alas ranjangnya adalah kayu triplek mknya bunyi, saran untuk penginapan semoga bisa di ganti, krna itu sangat mengganggu tidor. Yg kedua aku dapat kamar yg closet nya gk bisa siram otomatis + keran cebok nya jga gk fungsi ( gk keluar air sama sekali). Tv nya jga gk fungsi ( gk ada siaran sama sekali). Dan sandi Wifi-nya tidak langsung di beri tau ketika check-in. Untuk kebersihan ok, lokasi ok disamping RSUD Cut Nyak Dhien Meulaboh . AC nya ok, dapat handuk 2, dapat sikat gigi dan ada sabun jga . Shower nya ok. Air nya bagus jernih. Kamar mandi bersih. ",
      "reviewComments": "I got room 01, the bed makes noise when we move, even just a little. It turns out that when I checked, the bed base is made of plywood, which is why it's noisy. I suggest for the accommodation to change it because it really disturbs sleep. Secondly, I got a room where the toilet doesn't flush automatically and the bidet faucet doesn't work either (no water comes out at all). The TV also doesn't work (there's no broadcast at all). And the Wifi password wasn't provided right away during check-in. As for cleanliness, it's okay, the location is good next to RSUD Cut Nyak Dhien Meulaboh. The AC is okay, I got 2 towels, a toothbrush, and there's soap as well. The shower is okay. The water is clear and good. The bathroom is clean.",
      "reviewPositives": "",
      "reviewNegatives": "",
      "reviewerCountry": "Indonesia",
      "reviewGroupName": "Couple",
      "roomTypeName": "Premium Room",
      "lengthOfStay": 1
